data.title: Spring 2024 Dean’s List
data.meta_description: Wofford College announced the spring 2024 Dean’s List.
data.text:
SPARTANBURG, SOUTH CAROLINA—Dr. Timothy Schmitz, provost of Wofford College, has announced Dean’s List honors for the spring 2024 semester. Students achieving a 3.60 grade-point average or higher after earning at least 12 academic hours qualify for the Dean’s List.
